{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-requestProgress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The pack’s current progress."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","symbolKind":"property","title":"progress"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","abstract":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/progress":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The pack’s current progress."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"progress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflinePack"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgress":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A structure containing information about an offline pack’s current download"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"progress."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Posted by the shared ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","isActive":true},{"text":" object when an ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whenever any field in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"text":" property changes.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"}}}